{"tid":495973,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【fb=大台？】付費推po不似預期 「暗黑twins」寧用IG吸觀眾","createTime":"2017-12-11T08:51:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-11T10:34:02.000Z","uid":10958,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"68ad439ae3253a388c2f0f60300aadde53406402","tid":495973,"uid":10958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T08:51:03.000Z","msg":"<strong><br />\n【fb=大台？】付費推po不似預期 「暗黑twins」寧用IG吸觀眾</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://video.appledaily.com.hk/mcp/encode/2017/12/10/3501918/20171211_news_988_w.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvideo.appledaily.com.hk%2Fmcp%2Fencode%2F2017%2F12%2F10%2F3501918%2F20171211_news_988_w.mp4&d=OZLboJ8a3aGlrRIfUsiPBLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=406e5eab\" target=\"_blank\">https://video.appledaily.com.hk/mcp/encode/2017/12/10/3501918/20171211_news_988_w.mp4</a><br />\n<br />\n社交平台Facebook十年前在港開始流行，亦是港人現時主要使用的社交平台。有90後網絡組合認為，Facebook仍是眾社交平台之中影響力最大，「Facebook嘅傳播性最廣、最快，係得Facebook先做到」，但隨Facebook愈來愈多限制和廣告氾濫，認為Facebook旗下的Instagram（IG）是未來新趨勢。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171211/large/1512921951_603e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171211%2Flarge%2F1512921951_603e.png&h=55ceec58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">易欣（左）表示，曾試在Facebook付款「推post」，結果不如預計，吸引的觀眾群非她們的目標觀眾。馬泉崇攝 </span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171211/small/1512921953_4970.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171211%2Fsmall%2F1512921953_4970.jpg&h=0fadd2f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">陳樂兒（右）表示，平日拍片的題材都是取自生活，「好多時都係行行下諗到，或見啲人做啲搞笑嘢又會參考下」。馬泉崇攝 </span><br />\n<br />\n網絡組合「暗黑Twins」易欣和陳樂兒表示，相比其他社交平台，如Twitter、IG、Snapchat等，「Facebook嘅傳播率最廣、最快，係得佢先做到」。對於Facebook早前進行試驗計劃，若沒付費的廣告專頁帖文不會顯示在用戶的個人動態消息，易欣認為，無疑是阻礙她們接觸更多觀眾，又提到曾試過付款「推帖」，結果不是預計，「3、40蚊，但係啲印度人、中東、西班牙人like，呢啲完全唔係我要吸納嘅人」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171211/small/1512921956_6650.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171211%2Fsmall%2F1512921956_6650.jpg&h=9513ab28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">易欣（左）表示，其組合「暗黑Twins」現是以Instagram作為主要發佈平台，認為此平台更加國際化，及方便操作。馬泉崇攝 </span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171211/small/1512921959_bec3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171211%2Fsmall%2F1512921959_bec3.jpg&h=a7e0d2ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">陳樂兒（右）表示，Facebook愈來愈多廣告，已失去當初社交功能，現在身體朋友都轉到Instagram分享生活。馬泉崇攝 </span><br />\n<br />\n陳樂兒則認為，現時Facebook愈來愈多廣告，「好似美容公司啲激光療程，多咗好多呢啲suggest post，搞到你可能碌兩碌，第三個就係呢啲廣告，其實都會幾反感」，又指Facebook已經失去本身意義，「本身係畀朋友互相share下status（狀態），依家反而少左朋友嘅post、相，都畀廣告淹沒咗」。<br />\n面對「Like」字行頭的年代，易欣表明「暗黑Twins」是以IG為主，「因此IG相對較國際化，IG攞Like攞好多，啲人係攞5位數，Facebook比較少出現」；又指「其實我哋呢代係用多IG，IG都做到Facebook效果，好似（建立）個人形象」。陳樂兒補充，「IG（好處）係你會有一群觀眾睇，至少唔洗付費去push」。她們均認為，IG是未來新趨勢，「IG介面好方便，都係一張相加啲字，加啲hashtag（主題標籤）就post得」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171211/57565446\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171211%2F57565446&d=OZLboJ8a3aGlrRIfUsiPBLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=9a2c35cc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171211%2F57565446&h=3762a2b5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171211/57565446</a><br />\n<br />\n記者 張文鈴"},{"pid":"6618a590c700ec8e46251c2162a8dac09cd9118b","tid":495973,"uid":136994,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T09:37:40.000Z","msg":"IG咪又係FB旗下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc2aad9b9091410f3d3945706a53fb8f32ae36f6","tid":495973,"uid":55597,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T10:27:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>IG咪又係FB旗下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一鳩樣"},{"pid":"3806859c7306b249e80f6117b2cce505588c613a","tid":495973,"uid":389,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T10:34:02.000Z","msg":"都明點解無人理佢地"}]}